### Admin Panel - User Management

### List Users
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/users?page=1&per_page=20&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get User Details
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/users/user-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Activate User
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/users/user-123/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": true,
  "reason": "User appeal approved"
}

### Deactivate/Suspend User
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/users/user-456/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": false,
  "reason": "Violating platform policies"
}

### Change User Role (Super Admin Only)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/users/user-789/role
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "new_role": "admin",
  "reason": "Promoted to admin due to performance"
}

### Delete User (Super Admin Only)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/users/user-xyz?reason=Account%20terminated
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}

---

### Admin Panel - Order Management

### List Orders
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/orders?page=1&per_page=20&status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Order Details
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/orders/order-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Order Status
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/orders/order-123/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "note": "Order verified and ready for processing"
}

### Mark Order as Shipped
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/orders/order-123/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SHIPPED",
  "note": "Order dispatched with DHL - Tracking #123456"
}

### Mark Order as Delivered
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/orders/order-123/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DELIVERED",
  "note": "Delivery confirmed by customer"
}

### Cancel Order
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/orders/order-456/cancel?reason=Out%20of%20stock
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Admin Panel - Inventory Management

### List All Inventory
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory?page=1&per_page=20
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Low Stock Products Only
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory?page=1&per_page=20&low_stock_only=true
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Inventory for Specific Product
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory/prod-tomato?product_id=prod-tomato
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Add Stock (Receiving New Shipment)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory/inv-123/adjust
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "change_type": "ADD",
  "quantity": 250,
  "reason": "Received shipment from supplier",
  "note": "Supplier Order #SUP-2024-001"
}

### Remove Stock (Damaged Goods)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory/inv-456/adjust
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "change_type": "REMOVE",
  "quantity": 15,
  "reason": "Damaged during transport",
  "note": "Report #DAM-2024-005"
}

### Adjust Stock to Exact Level (Inventory Recount)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory/inv-789/adjust
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "change_type": "ADJUST",
  "quantity": 450,
  "reason": "Physical inventory count correction",
  "note": "Q1 2024 inventory audit"
}

### Get Low Stock Alerts
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory/low-stock/alert?page=1&per_page=20
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Admin Panel - Dashboard

### Get Dashboard Statistics
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/dashboard/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Admin Activity Logs
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/dashboard/activity-logs?page=1&per_page=20
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Logs for Specific Admin
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/dashboard/activity-logs?page=1&per_page=20&admin_id=admin-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Logs for Specific Action Type
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/dashboard/activity-logs?page=1&per_page=20&action_type=STATUS_CHANGE
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Notes for Testing

1. Replace `{{access_token}}` with a valid admin JWT token
2. Replace `{{super_admin_token}}` with a super admin JWT token for sensitive operations
3. Replace entity IDs (user-123, order-456, etc.) with actual IDs from your database
4. All requests require sending the Authorization header with Bearer token
5. Admin endpoints require the user to have "admin" or "super_admin" role
6. Super admin operations require "super_admin" role specifically

### Testing with cURL

Example cURL commands for testing:

```bash
# List users
curl -X GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/users?page=1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Update order status
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/orders/order-123/status \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"status":"CONFIRMED","note":"Order ready"}'

# Adjust inventory
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/inventory/inv-123/adjust \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"change_type":"ADD","quantity":100,"reason":"Restocking"}'
```
